,\"li\",\"967720ce9152\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"4e252fbb1cee0\",{\"children\":[\"The joy of rapid iteration with GROQ\"]}],\". Sanity.io offer \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"4e252fbb1cee2\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/docs/groq-reference\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"GROQ (Graph-Relation Object Queries)\"]}],\" as a way to filter your dataset’s documents, join them, and project the data structures that you need for your project. Like GraphQL it gives you one endpoint for all your content, but it’s way more versatile in the way you can shape and wrangle your data. After a couple of minutes, you can learn enough GROQ to be productive. With GROQ there is no need to loop over your data on the client-side after querying, you can shape it how you want it right in the query. This saves both bandwidth and processing time. \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"4e252fbb1cee4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/blog/we-re-open-sourcing-groq-a-query-language-for-json-documents\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"GROQ is open source\"]}],\" and can be used elsewhere as well.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"ac857c26da44\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"f8000bc6c2cc0\",{\"children\":[\"Great APIs.\"]}],\" In addition to GROQ, you can query your content with \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"f8000bc6c2cc2\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/docs/graphql\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"GraphQL\"]}],\". If you want to change a deeply nested value or change running text, you can do so with the powerful \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"f8000bc6c2cc4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/docs/http-mutations\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"mutations API\"]}],\". The \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"f8000bc6c2cc6\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/docs/realtime-updates\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"listener API\"]}],\" lets your apps subscribe to changes happening in your content in real-time. With the \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"f8000bc6c2cc8\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/docs/asset-pipeline\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"Asset pipeline\"]}],\", you can get on-demand image transforms. With the \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"f8000bc6c2cc10\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/docs/history-api\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"History API\"]}],\", you can browse document revisions and see who did what. \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"f8000bc6c2cc12\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/docs/webhooks_LEGACY\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"Webhooks\"]}],\" lets you integrate with other services.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"1c02b32c603f\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"60f152de9ae60\",{\"children\":[\"The calm of no-ops\"]}],\". We offer you a scalable backend, both in terms of the amount of data, but also traffic, security, and availability. \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"60f152de9ae62\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/docs/api-cdn\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"CDNs for assets and content delivery\"]}],\". Sanity Studio, the CMS, is a Single Page Application. We can host the HTML and the JavaScript file for you, or you can put it pretty much on any host. You can even deploy different studios connected to the same datastore if you want to build specialized editor experiences.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"8e80c9eb6199\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"0b6e3394738b0\",{\"children\":[\"Flexible, transparent pricing\"]}],\". You won't be forced to change tiers because of traffic or usage. \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"0b6e3394738b2\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/pricing\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"All tiers are pay-as-you-go with modestly priced overages\"]}],\". You can also add more datasets and users on all plans. The tiers differ on SLAs, support, and advanced features. There’s no hidden schemes or gotchas, it’s all on the website for you to scrutinize. We let you upgrade and downgrade whenever you want, and will prorate you for what you haven’t used if you downgrade before the month has ended. You don’t \",[\"$\",\"em\",\"0b6e3394738b4\",{\"children\":[\"have to\"]}],\" talk to sales ever (but we sure love to if you want).\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"efc861cba2eb\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"12cf600307170\",{\"children\":[\"Privacy and GDPR.\"]}],\" Sanity.io host your data in the heart of GDPR land: Brussels. Sanity.io is designed with GDPR in mind so that it is easy for you to stay compliant. None of your content is shared with third-party services (not even your images). We also offer custom edit history retention if your business requires that. If this isn’t enough, we also \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"12cf600307172\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/blog/a-rough-guide-to-running-a-gdpr-compliant-saas-business\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"blogged about how to run a GDPR compliant SaaS\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"9a9acc4dee4d\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"12245601a16d0\",{\"children\":[\"A content platform that has been in production since 2015.\"]}],\" Although Sanity.io is a relatively new product on the market, it has been used in production by companies such as the renowned architecture firm \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"12245601a16d2\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/case-studies/oma\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"OMA\"]}],\", and one of Norway’s largest media companies, Amedia. Publicly launched in 2017. Sanity.io is now used by thousands of developers and companies including \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"0fda6f062eba\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/customers/att\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"AT&T\"]}],\", \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"40e8def3484d\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/customers/tecovas\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"Tecovas\"]}],\", \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"7e0dfa3067ee\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/customers/amplitude\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"Amplitude\"]}],\", \",[\"$\",\"$L19\",\"b0b736d94caa\",{\"href\":\"https://www.sanity.io/customers/morning-brew\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[\"Morning Brew\"]}],\", and lots more.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"fbc03667027e\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"348e76282adc0\",{\"children\":[\"A tool for modern content strategy and design processes\"]}],\". If you look at the conversations happening within content strategy, you’ll quickly find \",[\"$\",\"em\",\"348e76282adc2\",{\"children\":[\"structured content\"]}],\" as a frequent topic. No wonder, since it’s a pattern that prevents duplicated content and tries to connect your text and media to the goals of your team and users. Sanity.io also makes \",[\"$\",\"em\",\"348e76282adc4\",{\"children\":[\"content-first\"]}],\" approaches to design easier with rapid content modeling and having the content available instantly. This is perfect when you’re building component-based design systems. Which you should be doing!\"]}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container py-12 lg:py-24 grid gap-12\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"aside\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$10\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",